{"tid":1604641,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"古羅馬野史 2   高地戰略要點   求推熱門","createTime":"2019-09-30T04:39:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T17:35:00.000Z","uid":164192,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"faf84925a374054c01bec875e9609828494ddb11","tid":1604641,"uid":164192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T04:39:24.000Z","msg":"野史分享<br />\n<br />\n羅馬帝制士兵經常喺民眾示威，佔領高地以制高點作視察同放冷箭，<span style=\"color: red;\">由於經常害怕高地有民眾投擲石頭</span>，<span style=\"color: red;\">往往都會先攻取所有制高點</span>，無後顧之憂，才展開驅逐和搜捕，而且當佔領高地後，由於距離限制，民眾只有俾箭射，捱打無得還擊。<br />\n<br />\n羅馬民眾經過多次磨練，總結出幾個要點，<br />\n根據野史記載:<br />\n<br />\n1. 焦土<br />\n古羅馬有多條橋樑，如果未有士兵看守，大多數只有旁觀民眾在橋上叫口號，未有任何作用，為了處理制高點，減少被佔領嘅風險，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>羅馬民眾用油倒在橋上，</strong></span>製造心理壓力，如羅馬士兵強行奪取制高點，火把將會是最後焦土手段。<br />\n<br />\n2. 勇武<br />\n羅馬有民眾不怕弓箭，以傷以死相博，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">經協調左右橋口齊上，直接飛卉衝向羅馬衞軍</span></strong>，作出主動攻擊，<span style=\"color: red;\">兩邊飛衝令羅馬士兵縮短思考時間，只有機會放兩箭，</span><span style=\"color: red;\">可悲的是兩箭必有死傷</span>，但士兵亦會成為籠中犬，而且勇猛民眾心知唯有奪回制高點，才可防止地面繼續高速推動，這個方法鮮有出現，但最有效大振民眾軍心。<br />\n<br />\n3. 弱點<br />\n高地制高點，極具遠距離進攻力，放箭投石，令人生畏，但<span style=\"color: red;\">由於高地容立人數小，逃脫選擇小，基本上被圍必敗，</span>所以沒有強力武器都不會強佔高地，難以自衛，勇武奪取必有死傷，但同時<span style=\"color: red;\">高地易攻難守，不宜久守。</span><br />\n正正大部份羅馬民眾過於良善，令衞軍憑幾把弓箭，就奪取戰略制高地，不怕被圍，也沒有心理壓力，因為民眾只是紙老虎，沒有反撲能力。<br />\n<br />\n以上都係歷史老師講嘅羅馬野史，<br />\n野史是真是假  勇武卻是童話<br />\n唯有舉起火把    否則只有捱打<br />\n<br />\n我唔支持暴力，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">千其唔好做暴力行因為</span></span>，野史真確性，見人見智。<br />\n<br />\n下邊 野史一 <span style=\"color: red;\">請熟讀流傳</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">一人一磚 護己救人</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n極重要 古羅馬野史  請求各位朋友聽下個故事 純歷史分享 求推熱門<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/efsdDS\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/efsdDS</a>"},{"pid":"85f5786880b98303170227febe31badb125aa9e7","tid":1604641,"uid":164192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T04:41:44.000Z","msg":"推  制高點要點"},{"pid":"b9c699ba3538e66753320bd81489d0e2f13dfba5","tid":1604641,"uid":164192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T04:42:22.000Z","msg":"居高臨下 <br />\n猛烈轟炸"},{"pid":"fdb6d3b09dc9efe417c9cc092fe0cc1c7b58106a","tid":1604641,"uid":164192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T04:43:24.000Z","msg":"焦土以油滑<br />\n橋樑被燒化"},{"pid":"3cfd6b5f6086a47a258650237ef5066349d0ded6","tid":1604641,"uid":280136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T04:44:05.000Z","msg":"［手足入］希望大家可以多D留意屋企樓下E個位，提防D奇怪人搵有用垃圾<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eftduS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eftduS</a>"},{"pid":"9b102fd1c2099f7d931a72f797e15c51a7d95c71","tid":1604641,"uid":164192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T04:44:37.000Z","msg":"高點被佔  令人生厭"},{"pid":"d85a43891cc31bed233f49937208dd7cfa5c491a","tid":1604641,"uid":164192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T04:46:10.000Z","msg":"唯有奪取戰略點高地<br />\n才可防止下方被遺棄"},{"pid":"1be696c153cfb8b4eae9a373b1bb01bd5d4b3296","tid":1604641,"uid":164192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T04:47:36.000Z","msg":"高地只有一個<br />\n誰得到誰有貨"},{"pid":"0d422432fb41a1cfc52ec28bb3931b1079fc60f3","tid":1604641,"uid":164192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T04:50:31.000Z","msg":"推 求推高地戰略"},{"pid":"6763839d1256c271713e08681de9c23f00a98f58","tid":1604641,"uid":164192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T04:57:04.000Z","msg":"推 高地"},{"pid":"a2fb0f1753a5aa376ca7313a66fe48759b23b3f0","tid":1604641,"uid":164192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T04:58:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1fa15ff813b15795d45a6668100922bca37b3fe0","tid":1604641,"uid":23023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T05:00:44.000Z","msg":"有個問題係要夠多真勇武<br />\n至少要20-30人一邊<br />\n唔係既話一定無可能隊到上去<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"212e5fcd0cb22bd5450c8c40a8c8e6c08f594386","tid":1604641,"uid":164192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1fa15ff813b15795d45a6668100922bca37b3fe0","tid":1604641,"uid":23023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T05:00:44.000Z","msg":"有個問題係要夠多真勇武<br />\n至少要20-30人一邊<br />\n唔係既話一定無可能隊到上去<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T05:16:39.000Z","msg":"羅馬必有勇士  高地衞兵心知民眾沒膽<br />\n可先公開召集 再一擁而上 衞兵沒法逃<br />\n<br />\n但必要兩邊飛跑直衝 以鐵牌當盾<br />\n令衞兵失去時間思考 放箭  但死傷難免<br />\n唯有盡量減少風險<br />\n<br />\n如沒勇武唯有用焦土方法  直接設油 必要時一燒就完<br />\n有前設 就沒有衞兵願意守橋"},{"pid":"109872a499200805fb88c823ff8b791869ebef93","tid":1604641,"uid":164192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T05:19:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"215ab8835c6c4e83065a22ee3b703d2bc62bd0fa","tid":1604641,"uid":164192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T05:56:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2683d4a1406ccb8d7bc64948f7c500288b6770ce","tid":1604641,"uid":171259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T05:57:34.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"13636bddc666572c3364d4e08f020a26810ed8d1","tid":1604641,"uid":164192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:18:33.000Z","msg":"推 歷史戰術分享"},{"pid":"8229fe97decfc494923727d9740444cb47166a51","tid":1604641,"uid":164192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:20:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"46b3901013b15c0bb232101457d7a3ebccb7b138","tid":1604641,"uid":164192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T09:53:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d8548a8ebded4a7f038a0c2f62df24741da8a963","tid":1604641,"uid":164192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T10:04:36.000Z","msg":"一人一磚 護己救人"},{"pid":"c555dbbe907d98054065c4ef3525224fbacea9bf","tid":1604641,"uid":207767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T10:07:03.000Z","msg":"推一推"},{"pid":"b4d9ad4195d9947c9226ef12db23f1c43beb70a8","tid":1604641,"uid":164192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T10:49:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bdf264dbbb84d88ae8c97abb45bc8b8520801092","tid":1604641,"uid":164192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T10:59:39.000Z","msg":"推 必須要多d 人知 我會繼續推"},{"pid":"7108242d5c99faf0026b1ba18700f39ec0b59507","tid":1604641,"uid":164192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T11:12:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1c37d91ffe1d98843aff6c7fee6867e72686a21d","tid":1604641,"uid":164192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T11:17:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"29b8cea2ce071d730c5bb95486cb09b34dd72023","tid":1604641,"uid":223609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T11:19:53.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"7bddafae1d71794a5e7f1d4f2e202fffe14f1f09","tid":1604641,"uid":164192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T11:23:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"27c1831231b7931c8fdd0b5d35c9f261e60dc17d","tid":1604641,"uid":286206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T11:30:04.000Z","msg":"用油守住一邊橋 佢地衝就射火魔法<br />\n<br />\n另一面橋就揾RB盡量拖時間走<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1705cfd781f76ea2525a28bf5f339e505cd06fa1","tid":1604641,"uid":164192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T11:40:23.000Z","msg":"前題 當士兵已佔橋 極小人以 文中第二點方式 有勇氣一擁而上<br />\n<br />\n根據第三點 易攻難守 橋下只要一失就被圍 橋上民眾就危<br />\n但士兵有強力武器 完全不怕以小戰多 最重要是市民是紙老虎<br />\n<br />\n所以第一點 預先放油 焦土據點 先最有用 大家都不用高地 直接地面戰<br />\n<br />\n當然 有高地 會有地利  令對方不敢推進"},{"pid":"c472c8fdae7041286a2c57278cf6f4e2be8bf8c8","tid":1604641,"uid":164192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T11:45:56.0